Wasted Food, Wasted Energy: The Embedded Energy in Food Waste in the United
States

     * Amanda D. Cuéllar
     * Michael E. Webber^*

   View Author Information
   Center for International Energy and Environmental Policy, The
   University of Texas at Austin
   Mechanical Engineering, Center for International Energy and
   Environmental Policy, The University of Texas at Austin
   * Corresponding author e-mail: [email protected]. Current address:
   Department of Mechanical Engineering, 1 University Station C2200, The
   University of Texas at Austin, Austin, TX, 78712.
   Cite this:Environ. Sci. Technol.201044166464-6469
   Publication Date (Web):July 21, 2010

