   Journal Logo

Effects of Proanthocyanidin Preparations on Hyperlipidemia and Other
Biomarkers in Mouse Model of Type 2 Diabetes

     * Young A Lee^†
     * Eun Ju Cho^‡
     * Takako Yokozawa^*^†

   View Author Information
   Institute of Natural Medicine, University of Toyama, 2630 Sugitani,
   Toyama 930-0194, Japan; and Department of Food Science and Nutrition,
   Pusan National University, 30 Jangjeon-dong, Geumjeong-gu, Busan
   609-735, Korea
   * To whom correspondence should be addressed. Fax: +81-76-434-5068.
   E-mail: [email protected].
   †University of Toyama.
   ‡Pusan National University.
   Cite this:J. Agric. Food Chem.200856177781-7789
   Publication Date (Web):August 9, 2008

Publication History

     * Received1 March 2008
     * Accepted19 June 2008
     * Revised2 May 2008
