       Compounds in Diabetic KK-Ay Mice. Journal of Agricultural and Food
       Chemistry 2013, 61 (27) , 6629-6635. DOI: 10.1021/jf401231j.
    2. Hsiao-Ching Lin and Shoei-Sheng Lee. Proanthocyanidins from the
       Leaves of Machilus philippinensis. Journal of Natural Products
       2010, 73 (8) , 1375-1380. DOI: 10.1021/np1002274.

