   38. Roberto Crosti, Antonella Arcangeli, Ilaria Campana, Miriam
       Paraboschi, Daniel González-Fernández. ‘Down to the river’: amount,
       composition, and economic sector of litter entering the marine
       compartment, through the Tiber river in the Western Mediterranean
