       Adherence of Microplastics to Soft Tissue of Mussels: A Novel Way
       to Uptake Microplastics beyond Ingestion. Sci. Total Environ. 2018,
       610–611, 635– 640, DOI: 10.1016/j.scitotenv.2017.08.053
