            Kolandhasamy, P.; Su, L.; Li, J.; Qu, X.; Jabeen, K.; Shi, H.
            Adherence of Microplastics to Soft Tissue of Mussels: A Novel
            Way to Uptake Microplastics beyond Ingestion. Sci. Total
